description._content: Creator: Poulsen, P. C. (Poul C.), 1857-1925 Description: Portrait of S. Yee, who is wearing formal, western style clothing, and is seated on an ornately carved chair. On his right is a small carved Chinese table, on which stands a jardiniere. His high crowned felt hat sits on a small carved table at his left. Location: Brisbane, Queensland. 27.470933,153.023502 View this photo at the State Library of Queensland: hdl.handle.net/10462/deriv/231719 Information about State Library of Queensland’s collection:www.slq.qld.gov.au/resources/picture-queensland
